{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/situs-e-book-mangamon-akan-ditutup/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Situs e-book MangaMon Akan Ditutup","content":"\n<p>Setelah beroperasi sekitar empat tahun lamanya, toko buku e-book MangaMon akan menutup operasinya di Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53633\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/situs-e-book-mangamon-akan-ditutup/attachment/01-mangamon-closing/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-mangamon-closing\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: MangaMon\" class=\"wp-image-53633\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: MangaMon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://www.mangamon.id/\" target=\"_blank\">MangaMon</a> merupakan platform toko eBook yang dioperasikan oleh eBook Initiative Japan Co., Ltd didukung oleh Elex Media Komputindo dan M&amp;C, sebagai bagian dari Kompas Gramedia Group. Situs ini telah mendapatkan banyak pengikut setia dari pecinta manga dan komik Indonesia dengan menerbitkan versi resmi dan berlisensi dari manga digital dalam bahasa Indonesia melalui websitenya dalam versi eBook.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sejak tahun 2015, situs ini telah hadir di Indonesia sebagai platform untuk membeli dan membaca komik digital secara legal, namun cukup disayangkan bahwa pada bulan Mei 2019 MangaMon harus berhenti beroperasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53634\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/situs-e-book-mangamon-akan-ditutup/attachment/02-mangamon-closing/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-mangamon-closing\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing.jpg\" alt=\"Tampilan situs MangaMon. Sumber: MangaMon\" class=\"wp-image-53634\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Tampilan situs MangaMon. Sumber: MangaMon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Melalui rilis pers yang diterima CIAYO Blog, terhitung pada tanggal 31 Mei 2019, situs ini akan resmi berhenti beroperasi. MangaMon akan perlahan-lahan menutup beberapa fitur utama hingga tanggal penutupan dengan timeline sebagai berikut.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>10 April: </strong>Fitur registrasi dinonaktifkan. Komik tidak bisa diunduh melalui Aplikasi Mangamon<br></li><li><strong>12 April:</strong> Fitur Top-Up M-Coin, membeli komik, menukar buku, dan download buku dinonaktifkan<br></li><li><strong>15 April:</strong> Hari terakhir penukaran Reward Point<br></li><li><strong>30 Mei:</strong> Situs MangaMon resmi ditutup</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53635\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/situs-e-book-mangamon-akan-ditutup/attachment/03-mangamon-closing/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-mangamon-closing\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: MangaMon\" class=\"wp-image-53635\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-mangamon-closing-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: MangaMon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama proses penutupan situs, pengguna masih bisa menggunakan beberapa fitur utama MangaMon seperti berikut.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Fitur Browser Reader</li><li>Fitur baca komik gratis melalui Browser Reader</li><li>Fitur akses Rak Buku melalui Browser Reader</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Buku yang sudah dibeli masih bisa dibaca sampai tanggal 30 Mei 2019 melalui Browser Reader. Lalu, situs ini juga akan melakukan <em>refund </em>kepada para pengguna yang telah melakukan pembelian menggunakan M-Coin di situs MangaMon dimulai dari periode 25 September 2015 s.d 10 April 2019. Proses dan jadwal refund adalah sebagai berikut.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>10 April:</strong> E-mail proses refund dikirim ke semua pengguna</li><li><strong>18 April:</strong> Hari terakhir konfirmasi permohonan refund</li><li><strong>1 Mei â€“ 15 Mei:</strong> Proses refund kepada Pengguna</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Informasi lengkap mengenai proses refund bisa dicek pada link <a href=\"https://www.mangamon.id/close/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"https://www.mangamon.id/close/ (opens in a new tab)\">https://www.mangamon.id/close/</a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e56ce7a0-d892-5d67-9bbe-b24f5757fec7"}}}